Kth LARGEST ELEMENT IN AN ARRAY - LEETCODE 215

Example 1:

Input: nums = [3,2,1,5,6,4], k = 2
Output: 5
Example 2:

Input: nums = [3,2,3,1,2,4,5,5,6], k = 4
Output: 4

CODE IN JAVA : 

class Solution {
    public int findKthLargest(int[] nums, int k) {
        Arrays.sort(nums);
        int index = nums.length - k;
        return nums[index];
    }
}
